# User Stories

## Employee

### Apply Leave
As an employee, I want to apply for leave so that I can inform my manager.

### View Calendar
As an employee, I want to view team leave calendar so I can plan work.

### Check Status
As an employee, I want to track leave status so I know approval outcome.

### Revoke Leave
As an employee, I want to revoke leave so I can change plans.

---

## Manager

### Approve/Reject Leave
As a manager, I want to approve/reject leave so I can manage team availability.

### View Team Requests
As a manager, I want to view all team leave requests.

### Bulk Approve
As a manager, I want to approve/reject multiple requests from calendar.

### View Availability
As a manager, I want to see who is on leave.

---

## System

### Maintain Balance
As a system, I want to update leave balance correctly.

### Conflict Warning
As a system, I want to warn users of overlapping leaves.
